{"tid":2389220,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"紐約年輕人號召重新佔領華爾街示威　抗議Robinhood限制交易","createTime":"2021-01-31T17:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T23:08:00.000Z","uid":63669,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"929561ff43bb6a000c82b935c29e697e33badbee","tid":2389220,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T17:19:45.000Z","msg":"這班年輕人的所屬組織紐約青年共和黨俱樂部（New York Young Republicans Club，NYYRC）29日在Twitter發文呼籲民眾「帶上標誌並穿上暖和的衣服，1月31日中午12時加入重新佔領華爾街的行動」。<br />\n<br />\nNYYRC主席瓦克斯（Gavin Wax）接受《紐約郵報》訪問時說，「過去幾天的事絕對是卑鄙的，這惹惱了很多人。精英和其他階層已無法與金融巨頭一同賺錢獲利。」他的言論顯然是針對美國券商羅賓俠公司（Robinhood）阻止用戶購買遊戲驛站等公司股份。<br />\n<br />\n瓦克斯表示，「我確實認為他們需要遭到起訴。當中很多人需要入獄。短訊和電子郵件必須被查封。這需要經過協調的行動以引起反響。」"},{"pid":"586ad2147b51d252fb93c85df674f60b746afbd2","tid":2389220,"uid":63669,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T17:20:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KHZ3SxXEQso\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKHZ3SxXEQso&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G0oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=488335e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KHZ3SxXEQso</a><br />\n<br />\nlive"},{"pid":"ddf4b4a62cf21b55ddc3aaa9373453e5dd973b3a","tid":2389220,"uid":97970,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"點解我登上左任美國仲亂左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f170a8f4947a1464ab996f147597d9b187380a64","tid":2389220,"uid":63669,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ddf4b4a62cf21b55ddc3aaa9373453e5dd973b3a","tid":2389220,"uid":97970,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"點解我登上左任美國仲亂左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\"